snippet.title: Polymega Gameplays - Arcade's Greatest Hits: The Atari Collection 2 [PlayStation - PAL]
snippet.description:
This compilation serves as a follow-up to the first Atari collection on the PSone. This time around, we get Gauntlet, Road Blasters, Millipede, Crystal Castles, Marble Madness and Paperboy.

Millipede, Crystal Castles © Atari SA
Gauntlet, Paperboy, Road Blasters, Marble Madness © Warner Bros. Discovery
Published by Midway Home Entertainment
Developed by Digital Eclipse
BIOS Used: Polymega BIOS
